Class AddMethodPrimitive

  • java.lang.Object
    • jmplib.primitives.AbstractPrimitive

        • jmplib.primitives.impl.AddMethodPrimitive
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Primitive

    public class AddMethodPrimitive
extends MethodPrimitive
    This class adds new methods to existing class source code. This class doesn't compile this code, only generates it.
    Author:
    Ignacio Lagartos, Jose Manuel Redondo
